metadata.name: Clone #1
metadata.description: PUBLIC MINT is Live: https://www.clonex.one. A Movement of the NFT community led by proud CX members. Become a Clone. As an Clone X member, you can own any of the 6,969 Clones, thoughtfully recreated into unique AI-generated Clone X Paintings. Only one painting will be minted for each Clone, and 24 distinct AI-models have been applied across the collection, to help create value for the owner of every individual ERC-721 token.
